<li><a href="http://www.newsweek.com/id/171261" class="external text" title="http://www.newsweek.com/id/171261" rel="nofollow">Middle East: Know the Limits of U.S. Power</a>, <a href="/wiki/Newsweek" title="Newsweek">Newsweek</a>, Published Nov 29, 2008, from the magazine issue dated Dec 8, 2008.</li>
